OL,3,CWelsh school choir stunned by
OL,4,Ccelebrity guest disguised as a statue
OL,6,FBritain's Got Talent's lead judge,
OL,7,FSimon Cowell, left pupils at Cardiff's
OL,8,FYsgol Glantaf stunned when he
OL,9,Fsurprised them on Saturday night's
OL,10,Fepisode of the show.
OL,12,FThe 70 boys from Glantaf school were
OL,13,Ftold they were singing at a statue
OL,14,Funveiling, honouring an important
OL,15,Fperson in the music industry. Once the
OL,16,Fred curtain was lifted, Simon Cowell
OL,17,Fwas revealed.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/5
