OL,3,CWelsh school choir stunned by
OL,4,Ccelebrity guest disguised as a statue
OL,6,FAt first, the pupils looked confused
OL,7,Fat the lifelike 'statue', but once
OL,8,FSimon shouted "surprise," the choir
OL,9,Fwent wild. Simon Cowell explained that
OL,10,Fthe choir would be auditioning for
OL,11,FBritain's Got Talent.
OL,13,FTheir choirmaster, Lloyd Macey,
OL,14,Fnominated the boys for the show. Lloyd
OL,15,Fwas a contestant on The X Factor back
OL,16,Fin 2017, where he made it to the semi-
OL,17,Ffinals under the mentorship of Louis
OL,18,FWalsh.
OL,20,FLloyd said he nominated the boys to
OL,21,Fboost their confidence.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,468,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F467A1776258665
OL,3,CWelsh school choir stunned by
OL,4,Ccelebrity guest disguised as a statue
OL,6,FThe choir went on to wow the rest of
OL,7,Fthe BGT judges with a rendition of
OL,8,F"Never Enough" from The Greatest
OL,9,FShowman.
OL,11,FThey received a standing ovation and
OL,12,Fyeses from all the judges, securing
OL,13,Ftheir place in the semi-finals.
OL,15,F"You should be proud of what you've
OL,16,Fdone, I actually got quite emotional,"
OL,17,FCowell said to the choir following
OL,18,Ftheir performance.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/5
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
