OL,3,CWelsh school choir stunned by
OL,4,Ccelebrity guest disguised as a statue
OL,6,F"This was just brilliant, this is what
OL,7,Fa great choir is all about ` having
OL,8,Ffun, great song choices, great leader,
OL,9,Fseriously," he said.
OL,11,FFellow judge Amanda Holden said the
OL,12,Fboys "did Wales proud and I can't wait
OL,13,Fto see what comes next," while Alesha
OL,14,FDixon called Lloyd Macey a "fantastic
OL,15,Fleader."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/5
